    "If you are reporting a bug, it would be helpful to attach the logs." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "af" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "As jy 'n fout rapporteer, sal dit nuttig wees om die logs aan te heg."
